\DOC metisverb

\TYPE {metisverb : bool ref}

\SYNOPSIS
Make {METIS}'s output more verbose and detailed.

\DESCRIBE
When this reference variable is set to {true}, it makes any applications of
{METIS}, {METIS_TAC} and related rules and tactics provide more verbose output
about their working.

\FAILURE
Not applicable.

\SEEALSO
copverb, meson_chatty, METIS, METIS_TAC.

\ENDDOC
